- proposed_change: Candidate corrective action pending mixed-group corroboration: add an L3 case-memory or pending note for ordered threshold scans with restart-from-match semantics, emphasizing that the procedure should update the reference pointer to the matched cell and resume scanning to the right until exhaustion. Also note the partial contradiction with the existing read-and-write-cells rule in this task's failures: some rollouts still wrote code text instead of the spreadsheet answer, but mixed-group evidence is needed before rewriting any existing rule.

